ishes the code list being referred to.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:length value="2"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_751"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d01b65e1ff311e1924f0026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>PID04| Product Description Code. NOTES: C0403 - If PID04 is present, then PID03 is required. R0405 - At least one of PID04 or PID05 is required. PID04 should be used for industry-specific product description codes.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:minLength value="1"/><xsd:maxLength value="12"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_352"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d01b65f1ff311e1cf160026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>PID05| Description</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:minLength value="1"/><xsd:maxLength value="80"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_752"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d01b6601ff311e196e90026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>PID06| Surface/Layer/Position Code. NOTES: Use PID06 when necessary to refer to the product surface or layer being described in the segment.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:length value="2"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_822"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d01b6611ff311e182990026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>PID07| Source Subqualifier. NOTES: C0703 - If PID07 is present, then PID03 is required. PID07 specifies the individual code list of the agency specified in PID03.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xs