ation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d17309e1ff311e189bf0026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>MSG03| Number. NOTES: C0302 - If MSG03 is present, then MSG02 is required. MSG03 is the number of lines to advance before printing. If MSG02 is "AA - Advance the specified number of lines before print" then MSG03 is required.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:minLength value="1"/><xsd:maxLength value="9"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element></xsd:sequence></xsd:complexType></xsd:element></xsd:sequence></xsd:complexType></xsd:element><xsd:element maxOccurs="25" minOccurs="0" name="L_SAC_3"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730e31ff311e1c06f0026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo></xsd:annotation><xsd:complexType><xsd:sequence><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="S_SAC"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730b11ff311e186710026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>Service, Promotion, Allowance, or Charge Information. To request or identify a service, promotion, allowance, or charge; to specify the amount or percentage for the service, promotion, allowance, or charge</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:complexType><xsd:sequence><xsd:element name="D_248"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a11ff311e19a870026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC01| Allowance or Charge Indicator. NOTES: If SAC01 is "A" or "C", then at least one of SAC05, SAC07, or SAC08 is required.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:length value="1"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_1300"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a21ff311e1cffc0026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC02| Service, Promotion, Allowance, or Charge Code. NOTES: R0203 - At least one of SAC02 or SAC03 is required.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:length value="4"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_559"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a31ff311e1c7380026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC03| Agency Qualifier Code. NOTES: P0304 - If either SAC03 or SAC04 is present, then the other is required.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:length value="2"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_1301"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a41ff311e1afc40026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC04| Agency Service, Promotion, Allowance, or Charge Code. NOTES: SAC04 may be used to uniquely identify the service, promotion, allowance, or charge. In addition, it may be used in conjunction to further the code in SAC02.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:minLength value="1"/><xsd:maxLength value="10"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_610"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a51ff311e1a6650026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC05| Amount. NOTES: SAC05 is the total amount for the service, promotion, allowance, or charge. If SAC05 is present with SAC07 or SAC08, then SAC05 takes precedence.</xsd:documentation></xsd:annotation><xsd:simpleType><xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"><xsd:minLength value="1"/><xsd:maxLength value="15"/></xsd:restriction></xsd:simpleType></xsd:element><xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="D_378"><xsd:annotation><xsd:appinfo source="http://sap.com/xi/TextID">8d1730a61ff311e1b2610026b9aa16ff</xsd:appinfo><xsd:documentation>SAC06| Allowance/Charge Percent Qualifier. NOTES: P0607 - If either SAC06 or SAC07 is present, then the other is required.</x